1
00:00:37,679 --> 00:00:39,159
I really like you

2
00:00:46,679 --> 00:00:47,359
I...

3
00:00:47,679 --> 00:00:48,359
I...

4
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:51,920
Help!

5
00:00:52,759 --> 00:00:53,280
Help!

6
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:54,600
Zheng Haiyang, Zheng Xiaochuan

7
00:00:56,119 --> 00:00:56,920
Hurry up

8
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:03,439
Quick, quick, quick

9
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:07,000
What's going on?

10
00:01:07,159 --> 00:01:08,280
What are you doing?

11
00:01:09,239 --> 00:01:09,719
Big Bro

12
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:11,680
He...

13
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:12,400
He's jealous

14
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:14,079
He drank too much

15
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:15,480
He's a bad drunk

16
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:16,719
You guys hurry and take him away

17
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:17,840
Take Big Bro away

18
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,799
Just take him back if he's drunk

19
00:01:19,799 --> 00:01:20,519
Let's go

20
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,079
Let's go, Big Bro

21
00:01:24,159 --> 00:01:24,680
Big Bro, let's go

22
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:26,280
Which one of you is Zheng Minjiang?

23
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:28,760
Who's looking for me?

24
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,280
Who are you guys?

25
00:01:31,959 --> 00:01:34,040
We're workers from Boss Tang's factory

26
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:36,480
We'd like to ask Master Zheng to come take a look at a machine

27
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:37,719
I am

28
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:38,799
No

29
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:42,400
Big Bro, should we go?

30
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,079
Go

31
00:01:47,079 --> 00:01:47,799
Go

32
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:49,439
Let's go

33
00:01:56,159 --> 00:01:56,760
Master Zheng

34
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,560
This way, please

35
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:03,319
You must be Master Zheng

36
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:05,799
You must be Master Zheng

37
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:07,200
Master Zheng

38
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,520
I've been waiting for you for a long time

39
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,840
Anyway, the money for breaking the machine...

40
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,360
I definitely can't afford to pay it

41
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,360
Might as well let Zheng Minjiang fix it

42
00:02:15,719 --> 00:02:17,960
Brother, what is the meaning of this?

43
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,639
Why did you send people

44
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,400
To tie us up and bring us here?

45
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,000
It wasn't kidnapping

46
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:23,560
Let go, let go

47
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,840
I just wanted to beg you, brother

48
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,000
To save my factory

49
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:30,719
My men don't know how to handle things

50
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,159
They were a bit anxious

51
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:34,120
You want

52
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:36,639
Me to help you fix the machine?

53
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:37,879
Yes, yes, Master Zheng

54
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:40,840
Uncle Tang, he can't do it

55
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,400
Look at how drunk he is

56
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,000
He doesn't look like a skilled worker at all

57
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,759
If he breaks your machine

58
00:02:45,759 --> 00:02:46,840
It won't be worth the loss

59
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:47,680
Yang Liu

60
00:02:48,159 --> 00:02:49,680
You don't understand Zheng Minjiang at all

61
00:02:49,879 --> 00:02:51,159
He has the skills and the ability.

62
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,719
He's not worthless like you said.

63
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,199
Are you a skilled worker?

64
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:55,560
Is it your place to speak up here?

65
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:57,439
It's not your place to talk either.

66
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,759
Stop talking.

67
00:03:01,759 --> 00:03:02,879
My dad hasn't even said anything.

68
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,520
Just think about it, everyone.

69
00:03:05,719 --> 00:03:07,520
If he really had that kind of skill,

70
00:03:07,719 --> 00:03:08,719
how could he fail to even get

71
00:03:08,719 --> 00:03:09,560
the position of Director?

72
00:03:09,759 --> 00:03:11,520
His family is poor as dirt.

73
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,360
Uncle Tang,

74
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,800
why don't you just wait for the German expert?

75
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,319
Don't get scammed by this guy.

76
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,000
Boss Tang,

77
00:03:19,319 --> 00:03:20,759
he's just drunk right now.

78
00:03:20,879 --> 00:03:21,599
Once he sobers up,

79
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:22,719
he can definitely fix it.

80
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:24,680
Li Guangming,

81
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,639
tell me, this Master Zheng,

82
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:30,159
how are his skills and ability, really?

83
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:32,879
Boss Tang,

84
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,639
that position of Director...

85
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,360
it originally belonged to Zheng Minjiang.

86
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:37,639
I got someone

87
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,520
to take his spot.

88
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:42,080
But he really has talent.

89
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,039
Minjiang,

90
00:03:44,199 --> 00:03:45,560
if you just fix the machine,

91
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:47,199
I'll give the Director position back to you.

92
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,439
I don't care about that.

93
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,199
I just hope

94
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:53,319
to work and live with a clean conscience.

95
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,520
You think I'm like you,

96
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,240
obsessed with being an official?

97
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,319
If you can't fix it,

98
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,759
just admit it and be done with it.

99
00:04:02,199 --> 00:04:04,080
Making excuses, pretending to be drunk...

100
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,400
Aren't you ashamed?

101
00:04:05,759 --> 00:04:06,280
Dad,

102
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,840
he simply can't fix it.

103
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,599
We've definitely been tricked by him.

104
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:11,800
Second Brother,

105
00:04:12,199 --> 00:04:13,599
what if Big Bro can't fix it?

106
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,639
How about I help Big Bro back home first?

107
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:18,360
Even if he waits to sober up tomorrow to fix it.

108
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,240
You have a point.

109
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,519
Big Bro really drank too much today.

110
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,680
Don't let him do anything stupid.

111
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,959
Hurry up and drag him back.

112
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,399
If they won't let him go,

113
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:26,079
I'll take the heat.

114
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,000
Hurry up.

115
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:27,920
Big Bro,

116
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:29,680
this machine is extremely precious.

117
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,319
If you don't fix it, you'll have to pay damages.

118
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,439
Let's not take on this mess.

119
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,199
Let's go.

120
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,000
You haven't asked him yet.

121
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,199
How do you know he can't do it?

122
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:46,759
Zheng Minjiang,

123
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,360
look at me.

124
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,839
You are a rare talent,

125
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,519
and now you just need a good judge of talent.

126
00:04:52,079 --> 00:04:53,959
This is the most important moment of your life.

127
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,319
Tell me, can you do it?

128
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:58,040
Of course.

129
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,879
Are you drunk too, Sister Yingrong?

130
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:05,000
Encouraging my brother like this.

131
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,319
Boss Tang,

132
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,600
my Big Bro really drank too much.

133
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,639
He's talking nonsense.

134
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:11,319
I'm not talking nonsense.

135
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,319
I can fix this machine.

136
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,240
And,

137
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,519
I can do it right now.

138
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:16,600
Good, good!

139
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,560
Zheng Minjiang, I support you.

140
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:21,959
Big Bro!

141
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:23,800
Big Bro!

142
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,120
If you don't fix the machine,

143
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,079
we'll have to pay for it.

144
00:05:26,199 --> 00:05:26,839
Our whole family

145
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,560
won't be able to pay it off in two lifetimes.

146
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:30,560
Don't worry.

147
00:06:10,199 --> 00:06:10,720
Hey.

148
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,560
Can you actually do this or not?

149
00:06:13,399 --> 00:06:14,920
If you can't, just admit it.

150
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,680
Don't waste everyone's time here.

151
00:06:17,079 --> 00:06:18,040
Exactly.

152
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,639
Look at him.

153
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,920
Fixing a machine,

154
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,560
and he's sweating all over.

155
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,959
He doesn't look like a man at all.

156
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,600
Quiet down.

157
00:06:26,879 --> 00:06:28,360
Can't you see he's fixing the machine?

158
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,560
What are you looking at?

159
00:06:32,759 --> 00:06:33,800
This machine...

160
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,879
is indeed a bit complex.

161
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:38,879
See?

162
00:06:38,959 --> 00:06:40,399
I told you he was a fraud.

163
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:41,680
Zheng Minjiang,

164
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,319
how could you be like this?

165
00:06:43,399 --> 00:06:44,519
If you can't do it,

166
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:45,839
don't try to be a hero.

167
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,959
If you break it,

168
00:06:47,399 --> 00:06:48,360
can you afford to pay for it?

169
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:51,199
Stop talking nonsense here.

170
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:53,560
Zheng Minjiang,

171
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:55,959
I believe in you.

172
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,399
Wang Yingrong,

173
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,040
are you defending him that much?

174
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:09,759
The two brothers...

175
00:07:09,759 --> 00:07:11,519
haven't even said anything yet,

176
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,759
and here you are, chattering away.

177
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:14,199
If you ask me,

178
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:16,079
you two must be in cahoots.

179
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,759
How about this?

180
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:18,959
You apologize to me,

181
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,199
and in front of everyone,

182
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:22,560
admit that you two are frauds.

183
00:07:22,759 --> 00:07:23,959
Pay us back the money,

184
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,800
and I might just let you off.

185
00:07:26,319 --> 00:07:27,240
Pay money?

186
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:30,120
Can money make up for our losses?

187
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,800
I want him in jail!

188
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,399
Done.

189
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,240
Is it really done?

190
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:48,319
How is that possible?

191
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:49,639
When I fixed it last time,

192
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,399
didn't it short-circuit and burn out?

193
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,319
The machine's central control system...

194
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,800
the inverter was burnt out.

195
00:07:55,199 --> 00:07:56,240
As for how I fixed it,

196
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:58,480
I don't need to explain the details to you.

197
00:07:58,759 --> 00:07:59,800
You are Director Li,

198
00:07:59,959 --> 00:08:01,120
my superior.

199
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,439
Just now,

200
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,519
you should have seen it clearly.

201
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:09,519
Boss Tang,

202
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:11,240
start the machine and take a look.

203
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,560
Okay.

204
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:29,240
Master Zheng really is Master Zheng.

205
00:08:29,959 --> 00:08:31,720
I can't thank you enough, Master Zheng.

206
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:35,039
I knew you could do it.

207
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:42,720
Is this Zheng Minjiang actually a talent?

208
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:45,159
How come I didn't see it before?

209
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:47,240
Master Zheng.

210
00:08:47,679 --> 00:08:49,600
Here is ten thousand in cash.

211
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:50,799
It's to thank you...

212
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:52,840
...as a reward for fixing the machine for me.

213
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,200
Boss Tang.

214
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,600
This is too much.

215
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,120
Not at all, not at all.

216
00:08:57,559 --> 00:08:59,559
I also want to sign an agreement with you.

217
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:01,799
Not a liability agreement.

218
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,120
It's that I want to invite you...

219
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:05,639
...to be a Technical Consultant at my factory.

220
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,799
About the Technical Consultant position...

221
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,200
...let me think about it.

222
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:10,759
But don't worry.

223
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:12,320
If the machine has any more problems...

224
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,799
...contact me anytime.

225
00:09:13,879 --> 00:09:14,799
Good, good, good.

226
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,919
Then I'll have Xiao Huo send the agreement over.

227
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,320
You think it over carefully.

228
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:19,720
But this money...

229
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,879
...you must accept it.

230
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:21,639
You have to believe...

231
00:09:21,879 --> 00:09:22,600
...you're worth it.

232
00:09:22,879 --> 00:09:24,759
And you're worth even more.

233
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:29,679
Boss... Boss Tang.

234
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,759
Zheng Minjiang fixed that machine.

235
00:09:31,879 --> 00:09:33,799
I don't have to pay that 500,000, right?

236
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:35,919
The agreement you signed...

237
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:38,000
...what does it have to do with him fixing the machine?

238
00:09:38,519 --> 00:09:39,320
Boss Tang, I...

239
00:09:39,919 --> 00:09:40,919
You have to pay what you owe.

240
00:09:40,919 --> 00:09:41,919
Boss Tang! Boss Tang!

241
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,759
Zheng Minjiang! Zheng Minjiang!

242
00:09:43,919 --> 00:09:44,960
Put in a good word for me!

243
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:46,759
Minjiang.

244
00:09:46,759 --> 00:09:47,279
Let's go.

245
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:47,759
Minjiang!

246
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,519
Minjiang!

247
00:09:49,519 --> 00:09:49,919
No...

248
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:50,960
Minjiang!

249
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,039
You think just because I'm down on my luck...

250
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,039
...that you'll be better off?

251
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,840
At worst, we'll both go down together.

252
00:09:55,559 --> 00:09:57,039
You... are truly useless.

253
00:09:57,399 --> 00:09:58,679
If you had found Master Zheng earlier...

254
00:09:58,879 --> 00:10:00,080
...would all this have happened?

255
00:10:00,679 --> 00:10:01,159
You...

256
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:03,000
...idling around all day long.

257
00:10:03,399 --> 00:10:04,080
Someone like you...

258
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,039
...still wants to inherit my assets?

259
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,879
Keep dreaming!

260
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:10,559
Boss Tang!

261
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:11,960
It's fixed!

262
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:12,440
Boss Tang!

263
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,440
A little less, please, Boss Tang!

264
00:10:17,639 --> 00:10:18,480
Honey...

265
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:22,879
I don't know how Zheng Minjiang did it.

266
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:24,840
He must have pulled some trick.

267
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,200
Go to hell.

268
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,120
Do you have any idea...

269
00:10:29,759 --> 00:10:31,240
...because of your nonsense...

270
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:34,360
...how long our factory's production was delayed?

271
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:36,360
How much loss it caused our family?

272
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:38,600
He...

273
00:10:39,799 --> 00:10:42,000
...how could he possibly know how to fix this machine?

274
00:10:42,559 --> 00:10:44,399
He grew up here his whole life.

275
00:10:44,399 --> 00:10:45,799
He's never even been anywhere.

276
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:48,399
How can he compare to that German expert?

277
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:49,759
Did you hear that?

278
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:53,120
My dad called me useless!

279
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:56,279
Said I'm not qualified to inherit the family fortune!

280
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:57,919
Are you satisfied now?

281
00:10:59,159 --> 00:11:00,039
No, Tang Yan...

282
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:00,960
Listen to my explanation.

283
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,919
I definitely wanted to help you.

284
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,000
Get off.

285
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:08,279
I knew you two had something going on.

286
00:11:08,919 --> 00:11:12,159
I heard that kid call you Sister-in-law the other day.

287
